lead_paragraph: Katie Hempen became No. 8 Arizona State's career leader in 3-pointers made and her 20 points Friday night helped the Sun Devils recover from blowing a big lead to beat No. 14 UCLA 65-61.

headline.print_headline: Hempen Leads No. 8 Arizona State Over No. 14 UCLA 65-61
